visionScore.description: (1 point per minute of ward lifetime provided) + (1 point per minute of ward lifetime denied).

visionScorePerMin.description: Vision Score is (1 point per minute of ward lifetime provided) + (1 point per minute of ward lifetime denied). So, Vision Score per Minute is how many of these points were accrued per minute.
